anyan Chandrasekhar">Subrahmanyan Chandrasekhar</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/D._K._Ray-Chaudhuri" title="D. K. Ray-Chaudhuri">D. K. Ray-Chaudhuri</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sarvadaman_Chowla" title="Sarvadaman Chowla">Sarvadaman Chowla</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <b><a href="/wiki/Halayudha" title="Halayudha">Halayudha</a></b><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <b><a href="/wiki/Jyesthadeva" title="Jyesthadeva">Jyesthadeva</a></b><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Katyayana" title="Katyayana" class="mw-redirect">Katyayana</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Narendra_Karmarkar" title="Narendra Karmarkar">Narendra Karmarkar</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <b><a href="/wiki/Madhava_of_Sangamagrama" title="Madhava of Sangamagrama">Madhava of Sangamagrama</a></b><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Prasanta_Chandra_Mahalanobis" title="Prasanta Chandra Mahalanobis">Prasanta Chandra Mahalanobis</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <b><a href="/wiki/Mahavira_(mathematician)" title="Mahavira (mathematician)">Mahavira</a></b><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Mahendra_Suri" title="Mahendra Suri">Mahendra Suri</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Manava" title="Manava">Manava</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Munishvara" title="Munishvara">Munishvara</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <b><a href="/wiki/Narayana_Pandit" title="Narayana Pandit">Narayana Pandit</a></b><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Jayant_Narlikar" title="Jayant Narlikar">Jayant Narlikar</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span lang="sa-Latn" title="International Alphabet of Sanskrit Transliteration" class="Unicode" style="white-space:normal; text-decora