yaya</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <b><a href="/wiki/Varahamihira" title="Varahamihira">Varahamihira</a></b><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Shankara_Variyar" title="Shankara Variyar">Shankara Variyar</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <b><a href="/wiki/Virasena" title="Virasena">Virasena</a></b><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Yajnavalkya" title="Yajnavalkya">Yajnavalkya</a></div>
